reviewText: "Listen to thed Music" is a good documentary of the Doobie Brothers story up to the reuniting album - "Cycles" -- in 1989.  It covers their complete history up till then, and has interviews with most of the former members of the Doobies.  It was great!  My only criticism was that the video picture was okay, but could have been better.

This is a good vhs of the Doobies some good concert stuff and interviews with the band telling why tommy had to stop working for a while and Mike got in the band! if you are a fan of the Doobies you will like this vhs ,
